<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>LegacyVerse</title>

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{
    min-height:100vh;
    overflow:hidden;
    background:
    linear-gradient(
    135deg,
    #020617,
    #0f172a,
    #1e1b4b
    );
    color:white;
}

/* BACKGROUND */

.sky{
    position:absolute;
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    overflow:hidden;
}

.star{
    position:absolute;
    width:2px;
    height:2px;
    background:white;
    border-radius:50%;
    animation:twinkle 3s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes twinkle{
    from{
        opacity:.3;
    }
    to{
        opacity:1;
    }
}

/* HEADER */

.hero{
    text-align:center;
    padding-top:80px;
    position:relative;
    z-index:2;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:5rem;

    background:
    linear-gradient(
    to right,
    #60a5fa,
    #c084fc,
    #f472b6
    );

    -webkit-background-clip:text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.hero p{
    margin-top:20px;
    color:#cbd5e1;
    font-size:1.2rem;
}

/* CITY */

.city{
    position:absolute;
    bottom:0;
    width:100%;
    height:350px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:flex-end;
    gap:20px;
}

/* BUILDINGS */

.building{
    width:100px;
    background:
    linear-gradient(
    to top,
    #111827,
    #374151
    );

    border-radius:10px 10px 0 0;
    position:relative;
    animation:rise 2s ease;
}

@keyframes rise{
    from{
        transform:translateY(300px);
    }
    to{
        transform:translateY(0);
    }
}

.building::before{
    content:"";
    position:absolute;
    inset:15px;
    background:
    repeating-linear-gradient(
    to bottom,
    #facc15 0px,
    #facc15 6px,
    transparent 6px,
    transparent 18px
    );
    opacity:.8;
}

.b1{
    height:180px;
}

.b2{
    height:280px;
}

.b3{
    height:230px;
}

.b4{
    height:330px;
}

.b5{
    height:260px;
}

/* LABELS */

.label{
    position:absolute;
    top:-45px;
    width:100%;
    text-align:center;
    color:#93c5fd;
    font-weight:bold;
}

/* CARD */

.info-card{

    position:absolute;

    top:180px;
    left:50%;
    transform:translateX(-50%);

    width:700px;
    max-width:90%;

    background:
    rgba(255,255,255,.08);

    backdrop-filter:blur(15px);

    border-radius:25px;

    padding:30px;

    text-align:center;

    border:
    1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
}

.info-card h2{
    margin-bottom:15px;
    color:#c084fc;
}

.info-card p{
    color:#d1d5db;
    line-height:1.8;
}

/* GLOW */

.glow{

    position:absolute;

    bottom:320px;
    left:50%;

    transform:translateX(-50%);

    width:300px;
    height:300px;

    background:
    radial-gradient(
    circle,
    rgba(168,85,247,.4),
    transparent 70%
    );

    filter:blur(40px);
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- STARS -->

<div class="sky">

<script>
for(let i=0;i<120;i++){

document.write(`
<div class="star"
style="
left:${Math.random()*100}%;
top:${Math.random()*100}%;
"></div>
`);

}
</script>

</div>

<div class="hero">

<h1>LegacyVerse</h1>

<p>
Every skill becomes a monument.
Every project becomes a landmark.
Every dream shapes your city.
</p>

</div>

<div class="info-card">

<h2>Your Digital Legacy</h2>

<p>
Imagine a city that grows every time you learn something new.
Your coding skills become skyscrapers.
Your achievements become monuments.
Your future is not a résumé — it is an entire universe you build.
</p>

</div>

<div class="glow"></div>

<div class="city">

<div class="building b1">
<div class="label">HTML</div>
</div>

<div class="building b2">
<div class="label">CSS</div>
</div>

<div class="building b3">
<div class="label">JavaScript</div>
</div>

<div class="building b4">
<div class="label">Projects</div>
</div>

<div class="building b5">
<div class="label">Dreams</div>
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
